this is a awesome movie. I watched this movie last night and it brought back some memories when I was little. not after watching it for years it had that same effect on me when I first watched it. this is a great movie. good animation, good songs and great characters and a good message as well preserve our rain forests. love this movie and the voice talents are great. if you have not seen this movie then I recommend you do
